name: ark-lost-and-found
topic:
Found someone's tame out in the wilderness? Help out the community by reporting it here. Be sure to utilize the form and provide a screenshot if possible. Note, tames posted here are not subject to being "adopted" by the founder, nor will they be given protections against the auto-decay timer.


**FOUND TAMES**
```
**FOUND**
Server: 
Cluster:
Tame Species: 
Tame Name:
Tame Tribe:
Coordinates: 
```

**LOST TAMES**
```
**LOST**
Lost On Server: 
Cluster:
Tame Species: 
Tame Name:
Tame Tribe:
Last Known Location/Coordinates: ```


**It is good practice to have a Soul Terminal (from the Dino Storage v2 mod) in your base, which will allow Ark Admins to return found tames to you.**

If the tame has been removed from the location, please indicate it in the forum post, or click on the ✅ emoji. Inactive posts will expire in 7 days.

name: ark-selling-trading
topic:
This is a forum for posting about things you are looking to buy or sell within Isla Nycta's Ark servers. When posting, remember to follow guidelines:

● Keep posts relevant to the Isla Nycta Ark servers.
● Please avoid creating multiple forum posts for duplicate ads. Posts will archive after 7 days of inactivity.
● Do not make posts for plugin-related content (Tame Paint Tokens, Nycta Ark Homes, boosted Auto-Decay buffers, etc.). 
● At this time, Nycta Tokens for transactions is **not allowed**.
● Posts involving the exchange of IRL currency of any kind (fiat cash, crypto, etc.) is not allowed.
● All arrangements between players are at their own risk; Isla Nycta reserves the right to be a neutral party and hold no liability in the event of dissatisfaction or dishonesty.

name: pot-nycta-mod-bugs-and-feedback
topic:
Nothing is ever perfect, unfortunately. Especially when it comes to mods! If you happen to find something that doesn't seem quite right, please go to the "reported bugs" forum and create a post!

To help us find these issues as quickly as possible, please consider the following before you make a new thread:

```yaml
VALUABLE INFORMATION TO PROVIDE:
```
▫️    What sub species of Nycta did you encounter the bug on? (Default, Spikey, Bald, Feathers?)
▫️    What platform was this bug experienced on? PC? Console?
▫️    What growth state was your Nycta at? Juvie? Sub-Adult? Adult?

```yaml
PLEASE ALSO CONSIDER:
```
▫️    PLEASE LIMIT EACH FORUM POST TO ONE ISSUE PER POST. If you have found multiple issues, make as many posts for each of them instead of cramming the issues into one post. This will help us with tagging, tracking, and closing out bug reports. 
▫️    Has someone else reported it? Use the search function to see if there's already an active thread. If there is a thread already, feel free to add to it! 
▫️    Use the provided 🔵  tags so we can narrow it down further; "animations", "sounds", "abilities" etc, etc. Non "blue circle" tags are for staff to utilize. 
▫️    Provide a video if possible! Videos will help immensely if you're unable to fully explain the bug. Screenshots may help as well.
